  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cats are Liquid - A Light in the Shadows is a minimalist 2D platformer about a liquid cat, locked in a world she doesn't quite understand, trying to get out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498330/extras/079b254471e080d27ec40988a06a5436.poster.avif?t=1759250354\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498330/extras/079b254471e080d27ec40988a06a5436.webm?t=1759250354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498330/extras/079b254471e080d27ec40988a06a5436.mp4?t=1759250354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The core of your movement is simple: move, jump, and climb, with your ability to turn into liquid allowing you to squeeze through tight spaces and dash across the rooms at high speeds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498330/extras/804eed7572f881f375d4bd7e06512fa2.poster.avif?t=1759250354\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498330/extras/804eed7572f881f375d4bd7e06512fa2.webm?t=1759250354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498330/extras/804eed7572f881f375d4bd7e06512fa2.mp4?t=1759250354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you play, you'll discover abilities which let you interact with the world in new ways. Break down walls and float high above the obstacles, all while mastering the skill of moving like a liquid cat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498330/extras/43fa1925b4ca168a501ece9bad658663.poster.avif?t=1759250354\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498330/extras/43fa1925b4ca168a501ece9bad658663.webm?t=1759250354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498330/extras/43fa1925b4ca168a501ece9bad658663.mp4?t=1759250354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The further you progress, the closer you'll be to discovering the true purpose of these rooms. Will you ever get out? </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cats are Liquid - A Light in the Shadows is a minimalist 2D platformer about a liquid cat, locked in a world she doesn't quite understand, trying to get out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498330/extras/079b254471e080d27ec40988a06a5436.poster.avif?t=1759250354\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498330/extras/079b254471e080d27ec40988a06a5436.webm?t=1759250354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498330/extras/079b254471e080d27ec40988a06a5436.mp4?t=1759250354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The core of your movement is simple: move, jump, and climb, with your ability to turn into liquid allowing you to squeeze through tight spaces and dash across the rooms at high speeds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498330/extras/804eed7572f881f375d4bd7e06512fa2.poster.avif?t=1759250354\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498330/extras/804eed7572f881f375d4bd7e06512fa2.webm?t=1759250354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498330/extras/804eed7572f881f375d4bd7e06512fa2.mp4?t=1759250354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you play, you'll discover abilities which let you interact with the world in new ways. Break down walls and float high above the obstacles, all while mastering the skill of moving like a liquid cat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498330/extras/43fa1925b4ca168a501ece9bad658663.poster.avif?t=1759250354\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498330/extras/43fa1925b4ca168a501ece9bad658663.webm?t=1759250354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498330/extras/43fa1925b4ca168a501ece9bad658663.mp4?t=1759250354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The further you progress, the closer you'll be to discovering the true purpose of these rooms. Will you ever get out? </p>",
